info.title: Altinn 3 App API for frontend-test ENGLISH
info.description:
This is the API for an Altinn 3 app. The API is based on the OpenAPI 3.0 specification.
This app has the following data types:
| DataTypeId | Type | Allowed number | MimeTypes | TaskId |
|------------|------|----------------|-----------|--------|
|message|FormData (AutoCreate)|1|application/xml|Task_1|
|fileUpload-message|Attachment|0-3|*|Task_1|
|ServiceModel-test|FormData (AutoCreate)|1|application/xml|Task_2|
|fileUpload-changename|Attachment|0-3|application/pdf|Task_2|
|fileUploadWithTags-changename|Attachment|0-3|*|Task_2|
|mainUploaderSingle|Attachment|0-1|*|Task_3|
|mainUploaderMulti|Attachment|0-5|*|Task_3|
|subUploader|Attachment|0-5|*|Task_3|
|nested-group|FormData (AutoCreate)|1|application/xml|Task_3|
|likert|FormData (AutoCreate)|1|application/xml|Task_4|
|ref-data-as-pdf|Attachment|-|application/pdf||
|datalist|FormData (AutoCreate)|1|application/xml|Task_5|

## This app has the following process tasks:
| TaskId | Name | Type | Actions |
|--------|------|------|---------|
| Task_1 | Utfylling (message) | data |  |
| Task_2 | Utfylling (changename) | data | fill, conflictingOptionsResetshiftingOptionsAddshiftingOptionsRemoveAll |
| Task_3 | Utfylling (group) | data | sortPets, generatePets |
| Task_4 | Utfylling (likert) | data |  |
| Task_5 | Utfylling (datalist) | data |  |
| Task_Custom_Confirm | Tilbakemelding (custom) | confirmation | reject, confirm |
| Task_Default_Confirm | Tilbakemelding (default) | confirmation | confirm |

post.description: The main api for creating new instances.

requestBody.description:
Instance document, formData and attachments

Any mime type that is not ``"application/json"`` or ``"multipart/form-data"`` with an instance document
will require the ``instanceOwnerPartyId`` parameter. Otherwise you must use the simplified instance document to specify instance owner.
Either using ``instanceOwner.partyId`` or ``instanceOwner.personNumber`` or ``instanceOwner.organisationNumber`` (or ``instanceOwner.username`` see [app-lib-dotnet/#652](https://github.com/Altinn/app-lib-dotnet/issues/652)).
